                      |1001 Nights: The Adventures Of Sindbad|
                      +--------------------------------------+

+----------------+
|Game Description|
+----------------+

Uncover hidden objects as you seek the seven precious stones of Princess Chalida's royal crown! Collect insects, solve dozens of riddles, and complete clever mini-games as you overcome scheming villains and break the powerful curse!

+----------------------------------+
|Instructions / System Requirements|
+----------------------------------+

No install or crack is required for this portable version. Extract the ZIP file and create a shortcut to the executable (EXE) to play.

- Windows 2000, 98, ME, Vista, XP, Windows 7

- 600MHz processor speed

- 64 MB RAM

- 32 MB VRAM 16 or 32-bit Video Card

- 16 bit DirectX compatible sound card

- DirectX 8.1

